If you use this software then you will become immortal. For the rest of your life, however long that may be, you shallbe chased by an immortal snail. If you so much as touch any part of that snail you will die immediately. Your soul will not be sent to either hell or heaven, instead banished to purgatory for eternity. The snail will now your location at all times and it cannot be contained no matter what. You cannot pick it up or move it through any means. Nobody else can see the snail except for you and there are no practical means of finding its location except through seeing it yourself. When you see it there will be no question in your mind that it is that snail. Proceed at your own risk.
